				<input type='password' placeholder='Password' name='password' ng-model='user.password' class='form-control'>
				<input type='submit' class='btn btn-primary' value='Login'>
			</form>-->
			<a href='/admin/register'>Register a new account</a>
		</div>
	</div>
  </div>
